snippet.title: Gex gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Gex, PC game produced by Microsoft in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/gex/2173/
Playing through a couple of stages in the first Gex platform adventure (2D)
Played through modern Windows machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Gex 3D: Enter the Gecko - https://youtu.be/Qxtf3cZ-Zls
Lion King - https://youtu.be/1Kc5jPdfHLY
Skunny Special Edition - https://youtu.be/YgZb87dnO0U
